mages/2008/10/20/4_presidents_2.jpg" title="4_presidents_2" alt="4_presidents_2" style="margin: 0px 5px 5px 0px; float: left;"></img></a>
While I've been thoroughly enjoying Election '08 both from the standpoint of riveted citizen and that of curious marketer, one thing that I've also enjoyed is all the fun.</p>

<p>And thanks to my friends at <a href="http://www.Glubble.com">Glubble</a>--most especially the extremely talented <a href="http://glubble.com/the_glubble_team">Bartel Scheers</a>--now we can all enjoy some Election '08 Memorabilia. </p>

<p>When he sent these to me, I swear it was like Christmas came early and thus I had to take a break from marketing posts to share the fun with my readers. Yup, you can download all four candidates and create your very own set of "Political Play Art Pals" (note: "Play Art" is a type of downloadable art that Glubble creates whereas you can construct all sorts of fun characters and creatures). 



</p>

